WEBVTT

00:03.945 --> 00:04.888
Who's my pretty girl?

00:06.638 --> 00:09.889
Eight, nine, ten, eleven.

00:11.411 --> 00:13.305
Sammy sweetie, don't get your dress dirty.

00:16.638 --> 00:17.779
Whoa! Hey, careful with that!

00:18.159 --> 00:19.301
Why don't you hand that to your brother?

00:28.895 --> 00:30.609
Our words can have a huge impact.

00:32.489 --> 00:34.970
Isn't it time we told her she's pretty brilliant, too?

00:36.974 --> 00:39.195
Encourage her love of science and technology...

00:39.723 --> 00:41.830
...and inspire her to change the world.

